What's the matter?

23
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,119
It's nothing.

24
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:47,200
Weiyi,

25
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,720
I have work to do.

26
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:50,400
All right then.

27
00:00:50,479 --> 00:00:51,240
You can go ahead.

28
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:56,759
Bai Zeliu,

29
