47
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:36,599
feel how tiny I am

48
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:37,559
and how mysterious the universe is.

49
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,480
So, you like adventures?

50
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,360
I do.

51
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,440
However, Weiyi, if you wish

52
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,279
for me to keep you company
at home every day,

53
00:01:44,919 --> 00:01:46,519
I will obey your wish.

54
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,319
Bai Zeliu,

55
00:02:05,639 --> 00:02:06,800
since you want to see the universe,

56
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:08,720
I'll prepare one for you.

57
